Program: Discovery
Title: San Diego Zoo
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxcj
Last Broadcast Date: 17 March 1999
San Diego Zoo has an international reputation for conservation science. The programme reports from San Diego Zoo which houses animals from all over the globe in spacious surrounds and employs more than 100 researchers in CRES (Conservation and Research for Endangered Species). One of its most popular inhabitants are the panda bears. Show less